snippet.title: Capcom New Super Mario Bros Wii Coin World Arcade - PlayNintendo.ca
snippet.description:
http://www.playnintendo.ca Capcom has released a very cool New Super Mario Bros Wii Arcade game in Japan. This is the video from the official webpage http://www.capcom.co.jp/arcade/coinworld/ . Downloaded and re-uploaded for your convenience. 

Learn more about this arcade game over at http://www.playnintendo.ca
